Special Forces (Mercenary)
Special Forces are the elite tier of the mercenary world: highly trained
multi-role operators capable of handling combat, infiltration, and demolitions
as the mission demands. They are expensive to hire and expensive to kill.

Special Forces choose from Military, Espionage, Weapons, and Physical skill
categories. Their training is broader and more intensive than standard
mercenaries. Many are former military from major powers who have gone
independent.

Attribute requirements: IQ 10, ME 10, PS 11, PP 11.
Starting equipment: Environmental body armor, CP-40 laser rifle, vibro-knife,
personal radio, demolitions kit, and a substantial credit reserve.
